{
  "stem": "5891.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What the heck's go-- what they going to do to me now?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in front of all those people, all the camp-- there was a reason for that, them doing that in front of all those people-- How many people?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Thousands?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had the whole camp, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh god, because they speak to the micro-- to the microphone, you know what I mean, to the monster.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The whole camp, then, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was lots of them there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had to walk there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I came from that thing, and the two Nazis there told me to get close to the bench and put my, from my waist, down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then he said, put your feet into this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now remember, there's a board there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your feet into this, and you're bending over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they take your hand, and you're tied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, you ain't going nowhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I figure, what they going to do to me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then they call-- he called out, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was supposed to get from the one or two, one, two, three, four. 150 is [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I stole the food from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as [? a solid ?] sign, that don't anybody ever get the idea that you could do this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I think I got about-- I should say, I got the hole here to prove this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They told me, maybe about 25 or 30.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Don't forget, they had that--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they had that short one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had one.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I wish I kept it, but I was afraid of that thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they had, it was real-- that-- that-- that SS thing, was with leather wrap.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in that, I don't know if your husband ever seen anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's round.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a lead thing in there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
